data.description: This delightful property offers a perfect blend of comfort and tranquility, surrounded by the scenic beauty of the area. This home offers many updates that add efficiency and reliability to this charming home including a newer septic field replaced 3 years ago and newer boiler replaced 5 years ago. Enjoy the fresh ambiance with new paint throughout, creating a bright and welcoming atmosphere. The property also features newer Pella windows, providing both aesthetic appeal and energy efficiency. Step outside to the expansive yard, complete with a fenced-in dog/pet enclosure, offering a secure space for your furry companions and a playground area surrounded by space for kids to run and play as well. Immerse yourself in the inviting atmosphere of this Wales Township gem, where the warmth of home meets the allure of rural living.
